_sText:
Created by Max, me.

This is the first edition of the map, I did some minor optimization/skybox things to it, but it needs further editing.

Things to do:
*Optimize more
*Make the roads to the bomb site more detailed
 -Make the road to 2 have a yard like area near spawn instead of just a wall
 -Make the tunnel to 2 go outside at some point, and link around behind CT spawn.
*Fix the overview to match up with the map. I left it out for FPSB, because it was distracting.
__________________________________________________________________

If you have any thoughts I would love to hear them, and please consider the above list when playing, if you do.

I hope you enjoy the gameplay, I think it is fun how I setup the sites. 

Any comments would be accepted, especially criticism.
